# VS Code Recommended Extensions

## Required Extensions
- **ES7+ React/Redux/React-Native snippets** (dsznajder.es7-react-js-snippets)
- **ESLint** (dbaeumer.vscode-eslint)
- **Prettier - Code formatter** (esbenp.prettier-vscode)
- **TypeScript and JavaScript Language Features** (ms-vscode.vscode-typescript-next)
- **React Native Tools** (msjsdiag.vscode-react-native)
- **GitHub Copilot** (GitHub.copilot)
- **GitHub Copilot Chat** (GitHub.copilot-chat)

## Optional but Recommended
- **Auto Rename Tag** (formulahendry.auto-rename-tag)
- **Styled Components** (jpoissonnier.vscode-styled-components)
- **Path Intellisense** (christian-kohler.path-intellisense)
- **GitLens** (eamodio.gitlens)
- **Color Highlight** (naumovs.color-highlight)

## Installation
Open VS Code and go to Extensions (Ctrl+Shift+X / Cmd+Shift+X)
Search for each extension and click Install.
